result.execSummary:
The defendant Sydney A. Kassube was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Sydney A. Kassube is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Sydney A. Kassube was found guilty of Possession of Narcotic Drugs [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime, Second and Subsequent Offense], a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(am).
  • Sydney A. Kassube was found guilty of Possession of Controlled Substance [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime], an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(b).
  • Sydney A. Kassube was found guilty of Possession of THC [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime], an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).
  • Sydney A. Kassube was found guilty of Possess Drug Paraphernalia, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.573(1).
